  "text": "14 Due to the α ′ -corrections, it is difficult to evaluate the BPS spectrum directly in the type IIA side. In [CITATION_1] , the authors instead used the Kontsevich-Soibelman formula that tells us how the BPS index changes in wall-crossings.",
